# Force LF line endings on checkout everywhere, including Windows.
# Two things depend on this: the canonical ledger serializer's exact-byte
# tests (template literals in test files must contain \n, not \r\n) and the
# CI bundle-drift guard (git diff --exit-code must not see line-ending churn).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary-ish artifacts git should never rewrite.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gz binary
.yarn/releases/** binary
